Xiaomi Router 3G AKA R3G
https://www.vvzero.com/2018/02/24/mi-router-3g-ssh/
https://jingyan.baidu.com/article/a24b33cd1080f719fe002b8e.html

1. download R3G developer version from http://www1.miwifi.com/miwifi_download.html
2. login your R3G router and upload that bin file
3. login R3G and login your Xiaomi account by MiWiFi App on your android phone
4. login http://www1.miwifi.com/miwifi_open.html and choose enable ssh tool download bin file
5. upload what your got from that website and do what it says
